  endingImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 19113d8eb8d17fc4e87fff8e471ac79a, type: 3}
  endingTitle: 'Bad Ending: The Third Interstellar War is coming!'
  endingText: "Ships slam into each other\u2019s paths, breaking formation as weapons
    fire lights up the dark. At the border, everything collapses into motion, ships
    weaving, colliding, pulling away only to dive back in. Signals spill out in languages
    the other side can\u2019t follow \u2014 but the anger carries, raw and unmistakable,
    enough for both sides to understand.\n\nThanks to your emphasis on anger in translation,
    everyone\u2019s fully caught up in it now. Wherever you go, you get shoved, kicked,
    and driven off \u2014 the two planets are at each other\u2019s throats now, and
    you are always seen as the other side."
  endingBgm: {fileID: 8300000, guid: a1d7402943db05247b87f738af4505f4, type: 3}
